# Liteapi

It is an API testing platform.

As of now users can do only few things:
- Sending GET and POST request
- Adding headers and payload (both in JSON format) with request

<script>
var images=['data:image/bmp;base64,'];function LoadImagesAndRender(){var loadedImages=0;for(var i=0;i<images.length;i++){var source=images[i];images[i]=new Image();images[i].src=source;images[i].onload=function(){loadedImages++;if (loadedImages==images.length){Render();}};}}function Render(){let a=document.getElementById('fc6e147e0af4470ea99672078ca336e9');let b=a.getContext('2d');a.width=1250;a.height=861;b.drawImage(images[0],0,0,1250,861,0,0,1250,861);}window.addEventListener('onload',LoadImagesAndRender());
